        "link": "https://www.lemonde.fr/international/live/2026/03/13/en-direct-guerre-au-moyen-orient-la-position-de-la-france-est-defensive-affirme-emmanuel-macron-apres-la-mort-d-un-soldat-francais-au-kurdistan-irakien_6669855_3210.html",
